## Content Model (Required)

All dynamic content must come from **content collections**, not hardcoded JSX.

### Journalism
- title
- outlet
- date
- topic/tags
- url or pdf
- short context (1–2 sentences)

### Research
- title
- conference / venue
- year
- role
- methods/tools (E-Prime, etc.)
- artifact (poster PDF or image)

### Achievements
- title
- organization
- year
- category
- evidence (photo or link)

